      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="observer-pairing-overview" data-step-uuid="76d9dfc5-3c75-4df9-ba47-ba28fd1fec16">
    <h2 id="observer-pairing-overview" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Observer Pairing Overview</h2>
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_66c68ca9-bb6f-4c24-b123-b8b60a2e7894" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Once you have pairing code(s) for your student(s), you can link your account to theirs. Guides below include steps for linking accounts. Whether you are linking your Observer account to multiple students at once or you’re adding a new student to your existing account, you follow the same process.</p>
